dc:description: Red micaceous clay with polished slip. Back half of lamp. On broad rim at either side of handle, moulded circle about circle of raised dots with dot in the center. From circles, row of short raised oblique lines runs along both inner and outer edge of rim. Raise band between rim and discus. Border of oblique lines about outer edge of rim. Solid ungrooved handle. Plain base.
